Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,譯者：微博@Emtee
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\fs13}Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這故事怎麽開頭的\N{\fs13}How does this story begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,和衆多故事的開頭一樣\N{\fs13}It begins like so many stories
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有一個少年\N{\fs13}With a boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,早不再是個小孩\N{\fs13}too old to be a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但仍年輕 遠未成年\N{\fs13}too young to be a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,此外還伴隨著一場噩夢\N{\fs13}And a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怪物召喚\N譯者:微博@Emtee
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,它有兩個基本常數\N{\fs13}It has two fundamental constants:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,e是自然對數系統的基礎...\N{\fs13}E, the base of the natural logarithm system...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,老樣子 放學見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,康納\N{\fs13}Conor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎 康納\N{\fs13}You all right there, Conor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你看上去很累\N{\fs13}You look tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有休息好嗎\N{\fs13}Are you getting enough rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊 我挺好\N{\fs13}Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想找人說說話...\N{\fs13}Because you know if you ever want to talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事\N{\fs13}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs13}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都朝前看\N{\fs13}Everyone, eyes front.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,當心啊 奧馬利\N{\fs13}Careful, O'Malley.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你會摔跤的 - 你是喝醉了還怎麽\N{\fs13}- You might fall. - Are you drunk or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他會找他沒什麽頭髮的媽媽要親親\N{\fs13}He'll have to get his slaphead mother to kiss it for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你總沉浸在你那小小的夢境世界裏\N{\fs13}You're always off in your own little dream world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那裏有什麽那麽有趣啊\N{\fs13}And what's there? So interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,放開\N{\fs13}Get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直都是個好孩子 好好記著 奧馬利\N{\fs13}You've been a good boy. Remember, O'Malley.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好孩子不會亂說話\N{\fs13}Good boys don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 康 - 嘿 媽媽\N{\fs13}- Hey, Con. - Hey, mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是什麽  - 一份驚喜\N{\fs13}- What is that? - It's a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 這是台VCR?  - 這可比VCR好多了\N{\fs13}- So this is a VCR? - This is much better than a VCR.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是你外公的老電影放映機\N{\fs13}It's your grandpa's old film projector.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了  - 真希望你能認識他\N{\fs13}- There we go. - I wish you could have known him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,誰\N{\fs13}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,外公\N{\fs13}Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.73,0:08:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就連你外婆對他都是溫婉可親\N{\fs13}Even grandma was softened up around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊\N{\fs13}Yeah, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs13}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真是群混蛋\N{\fs13}What a bunch of assholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他們爲什麽要殺金剛\N{\fs13}Why are they trying to kill King Kong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,人們不喜歡他們不理解的東西\N{\fs13}People don't like what they do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他們會害怕\N{\fs13}They get scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,金剛本可以把他們打得稀巴爛\N{\fs13}King Kong could've just smashed them all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,把他們幹成渣\N{\fs13}break them into a million pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,康納\N{\fs13}Conor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\fs13}Mum?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是來找你的 康納·奧馬利\N{\fs13}I have come to get you, Conor O'Malley.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你爲什麽不逃跑 康納·奧馬利\N{\fs13}Why don't you run, Conor O'Malley?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你爲什麽不爲了你媽媽逃跑 康納·奧馬利\N{\fs13}Why don't you run for your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,離她遠點 我不怕你\N{\fs13}You leave her alone. I'm not afraid of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,改天晚上我會再來找你 康納·奧馬利\N{\fs13}I will visit you again on further nights, Conor O'Malley...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我會晃你家墻晃到你醒\N{\fs13}and I will shake your walls until you wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,然後我會跟你講三個故事\N{\fs13}And then I will tell you three stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你要跟我講故事?\N{\fs13}You're going to tell me stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我要給你講三個故事\N{\fs13}I am. I will tell you three stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,等我講完 你要跟我講第四個\N{\fs13}And when I've finished my stories, you will tell me a fourth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我對故事一無所知\N{\fs13}I don't know anything about stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你要跟我講第四個 它會是真心話\N{\fs13}You will tell me a fourth and it will be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在說什麽 - 你藏著的真心話\N{\fs13}- What are you talking about? - This truth that you hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你夢見的真相\N{\fs13}The truth you dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你要把你的噩夢告訴我 - 不行\N{\fs13}- You will tell me your nightmare. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你會的 那會是你的真心話\N{\fs13}Yes. That will be your truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是不說呢\N{\fs13}And if I don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,康 我睡著了啊\N{\fs13}Oh, Con, I was asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你該在自己床上 康\N{\fs13}You should be in your own bed, Con.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就五分鐘\N{\fs13}Five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 夢不是真的 - 是的\N{\fs13}- That is not true. - Yes it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拜托 康 - 就五分鐘 我保證\N{\fs13}- Come on, Con. - Just five minutes. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,五分鐘\N{\fs13}Five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fs13}Night night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我尊重這點 麗茲 真的\N{\fs13}I respect that, Lizzie, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但你父親最不想的就是他被帶去美國...\N{\fs13}But the last thing your father would want would be for him to be taken off to America
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,....與某個陌生的女人和她陌生的孩子生活\N{\fs13}to live with some strange woman and her strange child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我們現在必須談談這事\N{\fs13}We have to discuss this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 康 - 小傢伙來了啊\N{\fs13}- Hey, Con. - Ah, there's the little man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你說你從哪弄到的 - 一家很好的養老院\N{\fs13}- Where did you say you got these? - From a very nice old people's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在收拾那裏 準備造公寓 我將是經紀人\N{\fs13}They're clearing it out to make flats and I will be the agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你的母親要一杯茶\N{\fs13}Your mother needs a cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,綠茶 不加糖 我要紅茶\N{\fs13}Green, no sugar. I take mine black.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得怎麽樣 康\N{\fs13}What do you think, Con?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他喜歡\N{\fs13}He loves it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 去吧 - 好的\N{\fs13}- Go on. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續試試別的\N{\fs13}Go on. Try something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我這麽做只是爲了你 - 我現在不想談\N{\fs13}- I'm only doing this for you. - I do not have this conversation now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白 但你不能再這樣下去了 麗茲\N{\fs13}I understand that, but you can not go on like this, Lizzie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你必須做出决定 - 我不會做决定的\N{\fs13}- You have to take some decisions. - I'm not doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,去幫康納沏茶 我要瘋了\N{\fs13}Go help Conor with the tea, or I'm literally going insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你和我得談談 - 我在沏茶\N{\fs13}- You and I need to have a talk. - I'm making tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 康納 - 我說了我在沏茶\N{\fs13}- Conor- I said I'm making tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是敵人 我來這裏是幫你母親的\N{\fs13}I'm not the enemy, Conor. I'm here to help your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我知道你爲什麽來 - 我來這裏是因爲\N{\fs13}- I know why you're here. - I'm here because...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,12歲的男孩不該自說自話地擦操作臺\N{\fs13}12 year old boys shouldn't be wiping down counters without being asked to first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想擦嗎 - 你太無禮了\N{\fs13}- You want to do it? - Less of your cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她在治療後總會發病\N{\fs13}She is always sick after her treatments.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,明天會好轉的 然後你就能回家了\N{\fs13}She'll be better tomorrow, and then you can go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她明天只會看上去好轉 她得跟你談談 - 跟我談什麽\N{\fs13}- She'll seem better tomorrow. She needs to talk about this with you. - Talk to me about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 談你來和我住的事 - 我絕不會去和你住\N{\fs13}- About you're coming to live with me. - I will never come to live with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 聽我說 康納 如果你母親... - 沒有如果\N{\fs13}- Listen to me, Conor, if your mother... - There is no if.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她會好轉的 然後你就能走了\N{\fs13}She'll be better and then you can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,麗茲 麗茲\N{\fs13}Oh, Lizzie? Lizzie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 堅持住\N{\fs13}My God. Hold on, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,藥在哪 康納\N{\fs13}Where's the medicine? Conor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,康納\N{\fs13}Conor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我來了 深呼吸\N{\fs13}I'm here, I'm here. Take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:20:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,康納 請把藥給我 快點\N{\fs13}Conor please. Please, give me the medicine. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,藥來了\N{\fs13}It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 好了\N{\fs13}Here you go, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs13}That's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,深呼吸\N{\fs13}Deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,深呼吸\N{\fs13}Deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,深呼吸 深呼吸\N{\fs13}Deep breath. Deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事了\N{\fs13}It is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什麽都別碰\N{\fs13}Just don't touch anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我 我會盡最大努力什麽都不碰的\N{\fs13}Trust me, I'll be doing my very best not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的談話還沒結束 年輕人\N{\fs13}Our conversation isn't over, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.02,0:21:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不 結束了\N{\fs13}Oh yes it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\fs13}Mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麽這麽慢\N{\fs13}What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.07,0:22:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是時候跟你講第一個故事了\N{\fs13}It is time for me to tell you the first tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.64,0:22:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要故事 我需要的是一張給我外婆的公車票\N{\fs13}I don't need a tale. I need a bus ticket for my grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.43,0:22:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是時候跟你講...\N{\fs13}It is time for me to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪 聽我說話\N{\fs13}Where do you think you are going? I will be listened to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.69,0:22:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我和這片土地一樣古老 我...\N{\fs13}I am as old as this land, and I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.71,0:22:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你都知道些什麽\N{\fs13}What do you know about anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.70,0:23:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你的一切 康納·奧馬利\N{\fs13}I know everything about you, Conor O'Malley.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.89,0:23:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道 如果你知道\N{\fs13}No you don't. If you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.57,0:23:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就很清楚我沒空聽一棵蠢樹講什麽蠢故事\N{\fs13}You know I don't have time to listen to stupid stories from a stupid tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.12,0:23:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這只是一個夢\N{\fs13}that is just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一個夢?什麽是夢 康納·奧馬利\N{\fs13}A dream? What is a dream, Conor O'Malley?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.77,0:23:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,誰又能說其他的一切不是夢\N{\fs13}And who is to say that it is not everything else that is a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.18,0:23:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,算了\N{\fs13}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我來見你是因爲我以爲...\N{\fs13}I came to see you today, because I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你以爲我會來打倒你的敵人 爲你殺掉惡龍\N{\fs13}You thought I might have come to topple your enemies, slay your dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我外婆的事 你至少得幫幫我\N{\fs13}Or at least help me with my grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,而你只是想跟我講故事\N{\fs13}All you want to do is tell me stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.87,0:23:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,關于我如何打倒我敵人的故事\N{\fs13}Stories about how I toppled my enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.73,0:23:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,關于我如何殺掉惡龍的故事\N{\fs13}Stories of how I slew dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.19,0:23:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我跟你講個故事 關于我何時會走動起來\N{\fs13}Let me tell you a tale of when I came walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.61,0:23:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我跟你講講邪惡女王的結局\N{\fs13}Let me tell you of the end of a wicked queen...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.45,0:23:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,以及我是如果確保讓她不再出現的\N{\fs13}and how I made sure she was never seen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.43,0:23:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,說吧\N{\fs13}Go on then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.55,0:24:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs13}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.45,0:24:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到了什麽\N{\fs13}What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.20,0:24:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,什麽也沒有 路上就樹葉\N{\fs13}Nothing. There are leafs in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.62,0:24:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,發揮你的想像力 康納·奧馬利\N{\fs13}Use your imagination, Conor O'Malley.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.30,0:24:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到了什麽\N{\fs13}Now, what do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.89,0:24:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我看到了火花  - 還有呢\N{\fs13}- I see a spark. - Yes. And?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.90,0:24:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 這是水 是水彩畫\N{\fs13}No, it's water. It is watercolor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.57,0:24:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續看\N{\fs13}Keep looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.81,0:24:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哇哦 - 確實會讓人驚嘆\N{\fs13}- Wow. - Wow, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.09,0:25:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,很久以前 這是一座城市 有道路 火車 汽車\N{\fs13}Long ago, before this was a town with roads and trains and cars...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.14,0:25:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 這裏是一個王國 - 這裏?\N{\fs13}- this was a kingdom. - Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.38,0:25:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我們這裏連樂購都沒\N{\fs13}We don't even have a Tesco.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.23,0:25:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這是一個繁榮的王國 有著一個睿智的國王\N{\fs13}It was a prosperous kingdom with a wise king...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.90,0:25:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,爲他的人民取得了和平\N{\fs13}With one peace for his people...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.15,0:25:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但和平是用某種代價換來的\N{\fs13}but peace had come at a price.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.99,0:25:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,國王失去了他全部的三個兒子\N{\fs13}The king had lost all three of his sons in battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.25,0:25:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,一個對戰巨人而死\N{\fs13}to giants
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.10,0:25:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一個對戰惡龍而死\N{\fs13}to dragons
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.26,0:25:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,一個對戰由大魔法師率領的軍隊而死\N{\fs13}to armies of men led by great wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.35,0:25:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這一切聽起來像童話\N{\fs13}This all sounds pretty fairytalish.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.42,0:25:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是聽到一個男子被矛殺害時的慘叫就不會這麽說了\N{\fs13}You wouldn't say that if you heard the screams of a man through by a spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.71,0:25:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,女王無法忍受喪子之痛\N{\fs13}The queen wasn't able to bear the loss of all their three sons...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.47,0:25:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,絕望而去 獨留國王一人\N{\fs13}Leaving the king alone in despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.50,0:25:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,和他唯一剩下的繼承人\N{\fs13}with the company of his only remaining heir...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.90,0:25:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他的孤兒孫子\N{\fs13}his orphaned grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.54,0:26:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子被撫養成了王子\N{\fs13}The child was raised as a prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.54,0:26:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,用他的勇敢和赤誠之心贏得了全國的愛戴\N{\fs13}winning the love of the kingdom with his scaventry and good heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.81,0:26:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他的人民敬愛他\N{\fs13}His people loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.44,0:26:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我們未來的國王\N{\fs13}Our future king.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.95,0:26:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他快成年時 他爺爺娶了新任妻子\N{\fs13}He was nearly a man when his grandfather took a new wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.97,0:26:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,可之後國王却病了 謠言開始蔓延\N{\fs13}The king felt ill and rumor began to spread...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.14,0:26:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,說她是一個邪惡的巫婆\N{\fs13}that she was an evil witch...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.23,0:26:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,說她給國王下了毒 想爲她自己奪取王位\N{\fs13}That she was bent on taking the throne by herself by poisoning the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.16,0:26:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,幾周後 國王死了\N{\fs13}A few weeks later the king died.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.60,0:27:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而王子還年輕 不能登基爲國王\N{\fs13}The prince was too young to take the king's place...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.27,0:27:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,因此根據法律 女王將統治一年\N{\fs13}So, by law, the queen would rule for another year.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.20,0:27:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,未來成了未知\N{\fs13}The future was uncertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.73,0:27:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,期間 王子有了心上人\N{\fs13}The prince meanwhile had given away his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.32,0:27:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她既漂亮又聰明 只是一個農夫的女兒\N{\fs13}She was beautiful and smart, and though only a farmer's daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.83,0:27:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,全國都覺得他們很般配\N{\fs13}the kingdom smiled on the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.63,0:27:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,然而 女王更享受當女王的樂趣\N{\fs13}The queen however, was rather enjoying being queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.06,0:27:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,除了嫁給王子還有什麽更好的辦法保留王位呢\N{\fs13}And what better way to remain so, than to marry the prince herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.40,0:27:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什麽 這真噁心\N{\fs13}What? That's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.57,0:27:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她是他外婆 - 是他繼任的外婆\N{\fs13}- She was his grandmother. - Step grandmother...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.24,0:27:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但還是一個年輕漂亮的女人 可別忘了這點\N{\fs13}and still a young, beautiful woman herself, don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.00,0:28:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,王子可不喜歡這主意\N{\fs13}The prince, however, didn't like the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.85,0:28:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他帶著農夫的女兒 騎馬逃至夜深\N{\fs13}He took the farmer's daughter, and they rode away into the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.78,0:28:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在紫杉樹的樹枝下停下休息\N{\fs13}They stopped to rest under the branches of a yew tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.20,0:28:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你\N{\fs13}That's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.87,0:28:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,第二天早晨 王子醒來\N{\fs13}The next morning the Prince awoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.21,0:28:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,起來了 我的愛人 他說道\N{\fs13}"Arise, my beloved" he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.55,0:28:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但農夫的女兒一動也不動\N{\fs13}But the farmer's daughter did not steer...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.91,0:28:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,而王子注意到了血\N{\fs13}Which was when the prince noticed the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.76,0:28:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,血?\N{\fs13}Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.69,0:28:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在晚上殺了他的愛人\N{\fs13}Someone had killed his beloved in the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.32,0:28:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,什麽\N{\fs13}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.66,0:28:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,女王 他哭泣道\N{\fs13}"The Queen" he cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.00,0:28:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,女王殺了我的新娘\N{\fs13}"The queen has murdered my bride."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.67,0:28:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,村民們滿腔怒火 復仇心切 他們暴動了\N{\fs13}The villagers, full of fury and vengeance, rose up at the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.34,0:28:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在那時走動了起來\N{\fs13}It was then that I came walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.95,0:29:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,女王再也沒有出現過\N{\fs13}The queen was never seen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.82,0:29:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 她罪有應得\N{\fs13}Good. She deserved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.58,0:29:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我外婆的事  我想你也幫不上忙\N{\fs13}Now, I don't suppose you can help me with my grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.15,0:29:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,故事還沒結束\N{\fs13}The story is not yet finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.18,0:29:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我把女王帶到了非常遠的地方\N{\fs13}I took the queen and carried her far enough away
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.29,0:29:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,人們永遠不會找到她\N{\fs13}so that the townspeople would never find her...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.20,0:29:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在海邊的一個村莊裏  她開始了新的生活\N{\fs13}to a village by the sea, where she began a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.60,0:29:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但她殺了農夫的女兒\N{\fs13}But she killed the farmer's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.82,0:29:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麽能救一個殺人犯\N{\fs13}How can you save a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.95,0:29:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的是一個怪物\N{\fs13}You really are a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.30,0:29:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我從沒說是她殺了農夫的女兒\N{\fs13}I never said she killed farmer's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.08,0:29:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我只說過王子那麽說的\N{\fs13}I only said that the prince said it was so.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.34,0:30:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那晚王子一直沒入睡\N{\fs13}The prince never fell asleep that night...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.09,0:30:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,却等著農夫的女兒沉眠于睡夢中\N{\fs13}but waited for the farmer's daughter to be lost in her dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.16,0:30:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,然後展開了他真正的計劃\N{\fs13}and then began his real plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.49,0:30:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什麽\N{\fs13}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.74,0:30:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道她的死會引發完全毀滅女王的星星之火\N{\fs13}He knew her death would start a fire that would consume the queen entire.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.04,0:30:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這故事太糟糕了 是騙人的\N{\fs13}That's a terrible story. And a cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.42,0:30:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這是一個真實的故事\N{\fs13}It's a true story.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.95,0:30:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很多真實的事物都像是騙人的\N{\fs13}Many things that are true feel like a cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.98,0:30:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,王國得到了值得擁有的王子\N{\fs13}Kingdoms get their princes they deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.51,0:30:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,農夫的女兒死于無辜\N{\fs13}Farmers' daughters die for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.07,0:30:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,而有時候女巫又應該被救\N{\fs13}And sometimes witches merit saving.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.75,0:30:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你會覺得驚訝 實際上 經常有這種事\N{\fs13}Quite often, actually. You'd be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.97,0:30:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以好王子是一個殺人犯 而邪惡的女王到最後却不是女巫?\N{\fs13}So the good prince was a murderer and the evil queen was no witch after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.98,0:30:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,女王當然是女巫\N{\fs13}No, the queen was most certainly a witch...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.90,0:30:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,也可能製造更大的邪惡\N{\fs13}and could well have been on her way to great evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.32,0:30:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢\N{\fs13}Who can say?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.96,0:30:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那你爲什麽要救她\N{\fs13}Then why did you save her then?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.58,0:31:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,因爲她不是凶手\N{\fs13}Because what she was not, was a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.59,0:31:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她沒給國王下毒\N{\fs13}She hadn't poisoned the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.93,0:31:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是年邁了\N{\fs13}He had merely grown old.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.10,0:31:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,王子有被抓起來嗎\N{\fs13}Did the prince ever get caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.04,0:31:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有 他成了一個受人愛戴的國王\N{\fs13}No. He became a much beloved king...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.69,0:31:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,開心地統治著 直到死去\N{\fs13}who ruled happily until the end of his long days.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.63,0:31:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\fs13}Oh yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.73,0:31:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\fs13}I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.67,0:31:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,誰是好人呢\N{\fs13}Who is the good guy here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.96,0:31:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不會一直有好人 康納·奧馬利...\N{\fs13}There is not always a good guy, Conor O'Malley...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.93,0:31:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,也不會一直有壞人\N{\fs13}nor is there always a bad one.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.04,0:31:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,很多人都介于這兩者之間\N{\fs13}Most people are somewhere in between.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.37,0:31:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這些怎麽從外婆那把我救出來\N{\fs13}So how is this all meant to save me from grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.80,0:31:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不是從她那把你救出來\N{\fs13}It is not her you need saving from.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.00,0:32:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,故事總有兩面性\N{\fs13}There are always two sides to a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.00,0:32:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你們有多少人知道一句俗話\N{\fs13}Now, how many of you know the saying:
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.37,0:32:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,棍棒和石頭可能會打斷我的骨頭 但言詞永遠傷害不了我\N{\fs13}"Stick and stones may break my bones, but words can never touch me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.72,0:32:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的話 下次要有人對你們說了什麽 只要記住...\N{\fs13}That way the next time someone says something to you just remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.81,0:32:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 你到家了\N{\fs13}Good, you're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.61,0:32:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你媽媽在樓上 她想和你談談\N{\fs13}Your mum's upstairs. She wants to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.94,0:32:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什麽 - 你爸周日會坐飛機過來\N{\fs13}- What? - Your father's flying in on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.83,0:32:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸要來了? 從美國過來?\N{\fs13}Dad's coming? From America?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.99,0:32:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\fs13}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.46,0:32:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,她等著呢\N{\fs13}She's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.83,0:32:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,打包好你的東西\N{\fs13}And pack your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.17,0:33:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你要來和我住幾天\N{\fs13}You're coming to stay with me for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.60,0:33:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\fs13}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.84,0:33:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那棵樹很贊\N{\fs13}That tree is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.26,0:33:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裏矗立了數千年\N{\fs13}It's been here for thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.39,0:33:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得怎麽樣\N{\fs13}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.75,0:33:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得外婆想把我變成蒂娜·特納\N{\fs13}I think Grandma is trying to turn me into Tina Turner.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.04,0:33:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她一定是她粉絲\N{\fs13}She must be a fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.42,0:33:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我爲什麽要和外婆住\N{\fs13}Why am I going to stay with grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.50,0:33:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你要回醫院嗎\N{\fs13}Are you going back to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.34,0:33:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,過來 康\N{\fs13}Come here, Con.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.18,0:33:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,上一次治療沒達到效果\N{\fs13}This latest treatment is not doing what it's supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.87,0:34:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所以要調整下\N{\fs13}So they're going to adjust it...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.51,0:34:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嘗試別的\N{\fs13}try something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.51,0:34:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-  就這樣? - 就這樣\N{\fs13}- That's all? - That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.02,0:34:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你確定嗎\N{\fs13}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.24,0:34:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,確定\N{\fs13}I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.38,0:34:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,因爲...\N{\fs13}Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.71,0:34:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你能跟我講的\N{\fs13}you can tell me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.43,0:34:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都會好的 康納\N{\fs13}Everything will be fine, Conor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.17,0:34:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你會看到的\N{\fs13}You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.41,0:35:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我們 康納 你要去哪\N{\fs13}Wait for us, Conor. Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.70,0:35:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不要碰他  - 不要碰他?\N{\fs13}- Don't touch him. - "Don't touch him?"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.24,0:35:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我給他臉上來一下怎麽了 - 我說了別碰他\N{\fs13}- With a punch to the face? - I said don't touch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.36,0:35:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,奧馬利和我有共識\N{\fs13}O'Malley and I have an understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.65,0:35:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我是唯一能碰他的人\N{\fs13}I'm the only one who touches him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.71,0:35:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,對嗎\N{\fs13}Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.96,0:35:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我\N{\fs13}Now tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.01,0:36:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,爲什麽每次我轉過身 你就在那看著我\N{\fs13}Why is it that every time I turn around, you're there looking at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.64,0:36:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你不覺得很怪嗎\N{\fs13}Getting a bit odd, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.69,0:36:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 這有點殘酷\N{\fs13}Sorry, that was a bit harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.16,0:36:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,今天 生活沒能如你所願 對吧\N{\fs13}Life isn't really going your way today, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.99,0:36:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我要帶人去看房子\N{\fs13}I have a house to show.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.05,0:36:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你會一個人待在這裏等你父親\N{\fs13}I trust you alone here till your father shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.37,0:36:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在不是五歲\N{\fs13}I'm not five years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.18,0:36:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這是正確的時間\N{\fs13}This is the correct time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.99,0:36:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你手機 電腦上都不對\N{\fs13}Not the one on your phone or on the computer,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.37,0:36:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就連新聞上的也不對\N{\fs13}not even on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.42,0:36:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我母親的 你曾外婆的\N{\fs13}That was my mother's, your great grandmother's.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.50,0:36:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,完美無誤地走了一百多年\N{\fs13}Perfect timekeeping for over a hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.11,0:36:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,康納 過來收拾好\N{\fs13}Conor! Pack up your rucksack.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.36,0:37:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望你父親覺得我讓你生活在猪圈裏\N{\fs13}I don't want your father to think that I'm keeping you in a pigsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.38,0:37:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真是沒什麽機會 - 是的\N{\fs13}- Not much shots of that. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.94,0:37:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,等你去了醫院\N{\fs13}When you go to the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.66,0:37:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你父親可能不會注意到你母親會有多累\N{\fs13}your father may not notice how tired you mother's becoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.22,0:37:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我們必須確保他不會待太久\N{\fs13}So we have to make sure he does not overstay his welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.88,0:37:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這跟以前的事無關\N{\fs13}Not that that's been a historically problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.99,0:37:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不能吃鶏蛋 這周你已經吃過兩次了\N{\fs13}No eggs. You already had eggs twice this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.19,0:37:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你餓了\N{\fs13}If you are getting hungry,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.81,0:37:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,冰箱裏有菠菜你可以蒸\N{\fs13}there is spinach in the fridge you can steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.40,0:37:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,當然\N{\fs13}Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.51,0:37:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,什麽都別碰\N{\fs13}Don't touch anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.43,0:37:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我會盡最大努力什麽都不碰的\N{\fs13}I will do my very best not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.07,0:38:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了\N{\fs13}Get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.91,0:39:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fs13}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.71,0:40:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麽樣 康 你看上去很累\N{\fs13}How are you doing, Con? You look tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.70,0:40:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我挺好\N{\fs13}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.36,0:40:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽在用新藥 會讓她好轉\N{\fs13}Mum's on this new medicine. And it will make her better.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.32,0:40:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她每兩個星期去次醫院\N{\fs13}She goes to the hospital every two weeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.03,0:40:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他們把藥物打入她的血流\N{\fs13}and they pump the medicine into her bloodstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.07,0:40:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,她會發病幾天 然後好轉\N{\fs13}She's sick for the next few days, but she's better again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.82,0:40:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你妹妹最近挺好  - 同父异母的妹妹\N{\fs13}- Your sister is doing better. - Half sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.45,0:40:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.78,0:40:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我想讓你和她見見\N{\fs13}I'd still love you to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.15,0:41:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你外婆談過了 想把你帶去洛杉磯\N{\fs13}I've been talking with your grandmother about bringing you out to LA.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.07,0:41:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想讓我去洛杉磯? - 是的\N{\fs13}- You want me to come to LA? - Yeah absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.99,0:41:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想去的吧 - 是的\N{\fs13}- You'd like that wouldn't you? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.41,0:41:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去那過聖誕\N{\fs13}We were thinking over Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.76,0:41:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,回來正好能上學\N{\fs13}that way you can be back here in time for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.75,0:41:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你意思是去玩咯\N{\fs13}So you mean just for a visit then?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.71,0:41:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊 會很棒\N{\fs13}Yeah, but it would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.29,0:41:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想和外婆住\N{\fs13}I don't want to live with grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.39,0:41:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那是個老女人的房子 裏面全是老女人的東西\N{\fs13}It's an old lady's house with old ladies' things.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.12,0:41:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你什麽都不能碰 哪裏都不能坐\N{\fs13}Can't touch anything or sit anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.17,0:41:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,連胡鬧兩秒鐘都不行\N{\fs13}Can't even leave a mess for two seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.38,0:41:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,康納 我知道 但...\N{\fs13}Conor, I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.25,0:41:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要自己房子的房間 自己的東西\N{\fs13}I want to have my own room in my my own house with my own things.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.52,0:41:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你來美國也不會有啊 康納\N{\fs13}Well, you wouldn't have that in America, Conor.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.09,0:41:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,幾乎沒足够空間給我們三個了\N{\fs13}There is barely enough room for the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.36,0:41:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不管  - 康納 聽著...\N{\fs13}- I do not care. - Conor listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.07,0:41:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她太嚴厲了 - 你的家人 你的生活 你的朋友...\N{\fs13}- She's so strict. - Your family, your life, your friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.53,0:41:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她家像個博物館 - 你的學校 一切都在這裏 好嗎\N{\fs13}- Her house is like a museum. - Your school, all of it is here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.41,0:41:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,把你帶離這裏是不公平的\N{\fs13}It would be unfair to take you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.24,0:41:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 對誰不公平 - 康納\N{\fs13}- Unfair to whom? - Conor.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.65,0:42:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你外婆好像還沒回家\N{\fs13}Doesn't look like your grandmother's home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.29,0:42:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,她有時會在我睡覺後再回醫院去\N{\fs13}She sometimes goes back to the hospital after I go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.82,0:42:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,護士讓她睡在一張椅子上\N{\fs13}The nurses let her sleep in a chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.49,0:42:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你外婆不喜歡我\N{\fs13}Hey, just because your grandmother
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.19,0:42:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不代表她是個壞人\N{\fs13}doesn't like me, doesn't make her a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.64,0:42:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,她說你總有始無終\N{\fs13}She says you're all start and no finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.91,0:42:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,她有權表達她自己的看法\N{\fs13}Well, she entitled to her own opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.41,0:42:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你會待多久\N{\fs13}How long are you here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.41,0:42:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,能多久就多久\N{\fs13}As long as I can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.24,0:42:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,什麽意思\N{\fs13}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.57,0:42:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我們錢不多 美國的假期也不多\N{\fs13}We don't have a lot of money and Americans don't get a lot of holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.77,0:42:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不是美國人  - 沒錯 但我住那了\N{\fs13}- You're not an American. - No, but I live there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.91,0:42:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,必要時 我會回來\N{\fs13}I'll come back whenever I need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.21,0:42:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,到了聖誕 你就來洛杉磯\N{\fs13}And you're going to come to LA for Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.15,0:42:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 你那小房子沒我空間了\N{\fs13}God no, not in your cramped house where there is no room for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.69,0:42:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,康納\N{\fs13}Conor
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.41,0:42:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹嘛要來\N{\fs13}Why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.41,0:42:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,康納 別走\N{\fs13}Conor wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.82,0:43:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,康納 明天見 好嗎\N{\fs13}Conor, I'll see you tomorrow, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.86,0:43:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,還有很多時間\N{\fs13}There's still loads of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.04,0:44:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這種破壞是相當值得同情的\N{\fs13}As destruction goes, that was remarkably pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.95,0:45:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,現在 我要跟你講第二個故事\N{\fs13}Now, I've come to tell you the second tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.97,0:45:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,和上一個一樣糟糕嗎\N{\fs13}Is it as bad as the last one?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.23,0:45:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是一個合理的毀滅結局 如果你是這意思的話\N{\fs13}It ends with proper destruction, if that's what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.02,0:45:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是關于一個隻爲自己考慮的男人\N{\fs13}It's about a man who thought only of himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.85,0:45:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一個理應慷慨却不慷慨的男人\N{\fs13}a man who wasn't as generous as he should have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.56,0:45:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一個受到慘痛懲罰的男人\N{\fs13}A man who gets punished very badly indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.98,0:45:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,故事都不是真實的\N{\fs13}Stories aren't real though.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.90,0:45:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,它們毫無幫助\N{\fs13}They don't help anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.19,0:45:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,故事都是狂野的生物 康納·奧馬利\N{\fs13}Stories are wild creatures, Conor O'Malley.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.11,0:45:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你鬆開它們\N{\fs13}When you let them lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.53,0:45:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,誰知道它們會造成怎樣的浩劫\N{\fs13}who knows what havoc they might reek?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.66,0:45:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\fs13}Oh yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.54,0:45:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs13}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.92,0:45:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,說吧\N{\fs13}Go on then.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.33,0:45:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs13}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.99,0:46:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,150年前\N{\fs13}150 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.37,0:46:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,未來降臨\N{\fs13}The future came.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.44,0:46:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,工廠如野草般生長\N{\fs13}Factories grew like weeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.78,0:46:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,樹木被砍 河水變黑\N{\fs13}Trees fell, rivers blackened...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.32,0:46:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,天空被烟灰弄得窒息\N{\fs13}and the sky choked on smoke and ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.18,0:46:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但仍有綠色存在 如果你知道去哪看的話\N{\fs13}But there was still green if you knew where to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.67,0:46:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在城市邊緣住著一個固執的男人\N{\fs13}On the edge of this town lived a stubborn man.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.80,0:46:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他拒絕改變\N{\fs13}Who refused to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.51,0:46:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他仍遵循舊醫學\N{\fs13}He daunted on the old ways of medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.51,0:46:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,使用草藥 樹皮以及用樹葉和漿果製成的混合物\N{\fs13}herbs and barks and concoctions brewed from berries and leafs.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.09,0:46:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,村民們稱他爲藥醫師\N{\fs13}Villagers ever only called him the apothecary.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.96,0:46:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什麽 - 藥醫師\N{\fs13}- The what? - The apothecary.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.87,0:47:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,藥師的舊稱\N{\fs13}An old-fashioned name for 'pharmacist'.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.11,0:47:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麽不直接這麽說\N{\fs13}Why didn't you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.12,0:47:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這村裏還有個年輕牧師\N{\fs13}There was also a young parson in this village,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.82,0:47:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很有見識 也很和善\N{\fs13}an enlightened man and a kind one...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.27,0:47:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一心只想著教區\N{\fs13}who just wanted the very best for his congregation.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.79,0:47:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他布道反對藥醫師的舊醫學\N{\fs13}He preached against the apothecary's use of the old ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.00,0:47:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,而藥醫師的壞脾氣和貪婪\N{\fs13}and the apothecary's foul temper and greed...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.12,0:47:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,讓那些布道更爲人所接受了\N{\fs13}made certain some of these sermons fell on eager ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.45,0:47:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他想盡可能地幫助社區\N{\fs13}Much as he tried to keep on helping the community...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.96,0:47:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但他的生意一落千丈 這讓他憤憤不平\N{\fs13}his business sank which only made him grow bitter
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.46,0:47:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,牧師的住所也有一棵紫杉樹\N{\fs13}On the parsonage's ground there also lived a yew tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.79,0:47:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你所在的地方\N{\fs13}That's the hill where you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.31,0:47:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,紫杉樹是最重要的治愈之樹\N{\fs13}The yew tree is the most important of the healing trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.32,0:47:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,爲什麽\N{\fs13}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.97,0:48:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,它的果實和樹皮 會彈奏 會燃燒 有著生命的悸動\N{\fs13}Its berries, its bark, they brum and burn and twist with life.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.62,0:48:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,能治愈幾乎所有疾病\N{\fs13}That can cure almost any ailment.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.77,0:48:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎 什麽都能?\N{\fs13}Really? Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.29,0:48:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,什麽都能 只要藥醫師混合得對\N{\fs13}Anything that can be cured if mixed by the right apothecary.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.62,0:48:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,藥醫師很想要這紫杉樹\N{\fs13}The apothecary wanted the yew tree very badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.22,0:48:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但要想獲得這些東西 就不得不砍倒它\N{\fs13}But in order to harvest these things, he would have to cut it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.25,0:48:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這是牧師所不允許的\N{\fs13}And this, the parson would not allow.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.54,0:48:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,牧師有兩個女兒  是他的生命之光\N{\fs13}The parson had two daughters who were the light of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.02,0:48:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他是一個充滿關愛的父親 爲了她們會給予一切\N{\fs13}He was a caring, loving father who would've done anything for their sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.62,0:48:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但有一天 兩個小女孩都被可怕的疾病擊潰了\N{\fs13}But one day both little girls were struck by a terrible sickness...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.72,0:48:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,而牧師做的一切都沒幫助\N{\fs13}and nothing the parson did helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.44,0:48:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,現代醫學沒有治療辦法 禱告也沒用 什麽都沒用\N{\fs13}No cure from the more modern doctors, no prayer, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.20,0:49:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,除了找藥醫師 別無選擇\N{\fs13}There was no choice but to approach the apothecary.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.18,0:49:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你願幫助我的女兒們嗎 牧師乞求道\N{\fs13}"Will you not help my daughters?". The parson begged.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.08,0:49:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你願拯救兩個無辜的女孩嗎\N{\fs13}"Will you not save two innocent girls?"
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.13,0:49:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我爲什麽要救呢 藥醫師說\N{\fs13}"Why should I?". Said the apothecary.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.83,0:49:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你的布道毀了我的事業\N{\fs13}"You have driven away my business with your preachings...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.26,0:49:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你拒絕把紫杉樹給我 那是最好的治愈之源\N{\fs13}and you have refused me the yew tree, my best source of healing".
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.45,0:49:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,紫杉樹你拿去吧 牧師說\N{\fs13}"You may have the yew tree," said the parson.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.34,0:49:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你會宣講讓你受益的事\N{\fs13}"I will preach sermons in your favour.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.23,0:49:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你救我女兒 我什麽都願意做\N{\fs13}I will do anything only you will save my daughters."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.54,0:49:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你願放弃你所信仰的一切嗎 藥醫師說\N{\fs13}"Would you give up everything you believe in?". Said the apothecary.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.83,0:49:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那樣能救她們 我就願意放弃一切\N{\fs13}"If it would save them, I would give up everything."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.55,0:49:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那我沒什麽能幫你的了\N{\fs13}"Then there's nothing I can do to help you."
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.82,0:50:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,第二天 牧師的兩個女兒都死了\N{\fs13}The very next day both of the parson's daughters died.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.84,0:50:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什麽  - 那天晚上我走動了起來\N{\fs13}- What? - And that night I came walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.29,0:50:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 他理應受到懲罰\N{\fs13}Good. He deserves all the punishment he gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.88,0:50:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯  那時剛過午夜\N{\fs13}Indeed. It was shortly after midnight...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.02,0:50:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,牧師家被我從底部往上撕裂開來\N{\fs13}That I tore the house of the parson from its very foundations.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.83,0:50:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,牧師? 你在說什麽\N{\fs13}The parson? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.73,0:50:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,藥醫師才是壞人\N{\fs13}The apothecary is the evil one.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.77,0:50:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他貪婪粗魯 但他仍是個治療者\N{\fs13}He was greedy and rude, but he was still a healer.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.79,0:50:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,而牧師 他是什麽呢\N{\fs13}The parson, what was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.52,0:50:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,一個沒有信仰的信徒\N{\fs13}A man of faith without faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.76,0:51:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,信念是半個救治方式\N{\fs13}Belief is half of all healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.44,0:51:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,相信治療方式 相信等待著的未來\N{\fs13}Belief in the cure, belief in the future that awaits.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.66,0:51:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,信仰是寶貴的\N{\fs13}Your belief is precious...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.86,0:51:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你應該留意你信仰什麽 你信仰誰\N{\fs13}so you must be careful where you put it and in whom.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.49,0:51:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我 康納·奧馬利 下一個我要毀掉什麽\N{\fs13}Tell me, Conor O'Malley, what shall I destroy next?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.34,0:51:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什麽 - 這很爽 我向你保證 快\N{\fs13}- What? - It is most satisfying, I can assure you.Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.80,0:51:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我 我要毀掉什麽\N{\fs13}Tell me. What should I destroy?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.04,0:51:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,打壞烟囪\N{\fs13}Smack the chimney?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.84,0:51:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,烟囪\N{\fs13}The chimney.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.90,0:51:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,下面呢\N{\fs13}Next?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.86,0:51:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,扔掉他們的床\N{\fs13}Throw away their beds.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.39,0:51:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,打破家具\N{\fs13}Smash the furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.89,0:51:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,打破窗戶\N{\fs13}Break the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.20,0:51:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,窗戶?\N{\fs13}Windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.30,0:51:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你來親自動手吧\N{\fs13}Break them yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.68,0:52:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧\N{\fs13}Come one.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.03,0:52:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,再用力些  康納·奧馬利\N{\fs13}Harder, Conor O'Malley.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.35,0:52:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,再用力些\N{\fs13}Come on. Harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.16,0:52:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣\N{\fs13}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.49,0:52:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\fs13}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.12,0:52:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺很棒吧\N{\fs13}Feels good doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.71,0:52:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.83,0:54:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,外婆\N{\fs13}Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.53,0:54:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,外婆\N{\fs13}Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.26,0:54:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,外婆 別這樣\N{\fs13}Grandma, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.48,0:55:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,外婆\N{\fs13}Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.32,0:56:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽說你喜歡吃煎蛋\N{\fs13}I heard you like them sunny side up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.51,0:56:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-  你在這裏幹嘛 - 你覺得呢\N{\fs13}- What are you doing here? - What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.32,0:56:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你外婆今天一大早就打電話來了\N{\fs13}Your grandmother called very early this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.13,0:56:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,她去醫院看你媽媽了\N{\fs13}She's gone to the hospital to see your mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.15,0:56:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你媽媽惡化了 康\N{\fs13}Your mum's had a bad turn, Con.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.89,0:56:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我要見她\N{\fs13}I need to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.08,0:56:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我們到時候看今天的結果\N{\fs13}We'll see what happens today, and maybe you can
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.10,0:56:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,也許你下午能去看她一會兒\N{\fs13}visit for a little while this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.19,0:56:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你有多難過\N{\fs13}I can see how upset you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.43,0:56:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是故意的 我不知道怎麽回事\N{\fs13}I didn't mean to. I don't know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.11,0:56:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在海上有更糟的事  - 什麽意思\N{\fs13}- Worse things happen at sea. - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.41,0:56:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你要懲罰我嗎\N{\fs13}Aren't you going to punish me?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.28,0:56:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這有什麽意義\N{\fs13}What could possibly be the point in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.47,0:57:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須說 這真的是令人驚訝\N{\fs13}I got to say champ, this is really just amazingly thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.65,0:57:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,一個被掩埋的寶藏\N{\fs13}Oh, a buried treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.64,0:57:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這一定是我第一次搬走時\N{\fs13}These must be those home movies that your mother
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.37,0:57:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你媽寄我的家庭電影\N{\fs13}used to send when I first moved away.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.90,0:57:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你爲什麽搬走\N{\fs13}Why did you move away?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.97,0:57:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我們當時還年輕\N{\fs13}We were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.07,0:57:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,很年輕 我們有很大的夢想\N{\fs13}Too young, you know? We had big dreams, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.13,0:57:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什麽樣的夢想 - 你媽媽想去藝術學校\N{\fs13}- What kind of dreams? - Your mother wanted to go to art college.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.91,0:57:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是嗎 - 沒錯 她沒去 但她想去\N{\fs13}- Really? - Yeah. She didn't go, but she wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.76,0:57:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,發生了什麽事\N{\fs13}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.18,0:57:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,因爲媽媽懷了我\N{\fs13}Because mum got pregnant with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.03,0:57:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你媽媽從沒後悔有了你 你是唯一的好消息\N{\fs13}Mum never regretted having you. You were only ever good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.31,0:57:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我很清楚 因爲她後悔一件事 就是嫁給了我\N{\fs13}And I know that for a fact, because the one thing she regretted was marrying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.80,0:58:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那她爲什麽要嫁給你 - 因爲我帥\N{\fs13}- Why did she marry you then? - Because I'm handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.39,0:58:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你媽媽很棒 現在還是 當時我們戀愛了\N{\fs13}Your mum was amazing. And she still is. And we were in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.94,0:58:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我還愛她 但你會知道...\N{\fs13}I mean, I still love her. But you will see that...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.09,0:58:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,愛是不够的 它沒法帶你度過一生\N{\fs13}love isn't enough. It doesn't carry you through.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.99,0:58:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你後來就沒有幸福過\N{\fs13}So you didn't get happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.90,0:58:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 但這就是生活\N{\fs13}No, but that's life, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.81,0:58:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,多數情况就是變得更糟了 但沒關係\N{\fs13}Most of it just get messier after. And that's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.14,0:58:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高興你變得像她\N{\fs13}Even I'm happy you turned out like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.02,0:59:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,錢德勒夫人\N{\fs13}Mrs Chandler.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.65,0:59:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,教育很重要\N{\fs13}Education is really important!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.43,0:59:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我又不是不知道 我各方面都很節省了\N{\fs13}You're telling me now what to do. I'm pulled in every direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.01,0:59:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那你是要讓他不上學了嗎\N{\fs13}Are you going to take him out of school then?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.62,0:59:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fs13}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.78,1:00:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我想找點吃的 你呢 孩子\N{\fs13}I'm looking for something to eat. You want something, kid?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.06,1:00:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,別叫我孩子\N{\fs13}Stop calling me 'kid'.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.53,1:00:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs13}Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.70,1:00:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 麗茲\N{\fs13}I'm sorry, Lizzie.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.27,1:00:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,穿西裝的那男人是誰\N{\fs13}Who was that man in a suit?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.93,1:00:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,只是...\N{\fs13}Just...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.59,1:00:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麽\N{\fs13}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.81,1:00:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 今天上午發生了什麽  - 沒什麽\N{\fs13}- What happened this morning? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.18,1:00:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的\N{\fs13}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.23,1:00:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是有點不好的反應\N{\fs13}I had a bit of a bad reaction.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.64,1:00:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但他們還會做一個嘗試\N{\fs13}There's one more thing they're going to try,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.95,1:00:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那種藥的效果真的很好\N{\fs13}and it's a medicine that's had some really good results.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.05,1:00:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他們爲什麽不一開始就試呢\N{\fs13}Why didn't they try it in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.28,1:00:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,因爲你用了別的東西\N{\fs13}Because this is something you take when the other
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.86,1:00:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,然而效果不如他們所想的那麽好\N{\fs13}stuff hasn't worked the way they wanted it to.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.66,1:00:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,意思太遲了嗎\N{\fs13}Does that mean it's too late?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.37,1:01:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,當然不是太遲的意思\N{\fs13}No of course it doesn't mean it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.65,1:01:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你確定嗎\N{\fs13}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.41,1:01:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信我說的每一個字\N{\fs13}I believe every word I say.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.60,1:01:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,信念是半個救治方式\N{\fs13}Belief is half of all healing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.00,1:01:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,相信治療方式 相信等待著的未來\N{\fs13}Belief in the cure, belief in the future that awaits.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.57,1:01:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.06,1:01:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你還記得我一直說的那棵樹嗎\N{\fs13}And you know that tree I'm always going on about?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.22,1:01:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,記得\N{\fs13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.88,1:01:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這藥是拿那種樹做的\N{\fs13}Well, this drug is made from trees like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.61,1:01:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是嗎 - 沒錯\N{\fs13}- It is? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.20,1:01:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真的?\N{\fs13}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.76,1:01:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以來 我們本能出去砍掉它\N{\fs13}All this time we could have gone out there and just chopped it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.29,1:01:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但那一棵不行\N{\fs13}But not that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.27,1:01:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那一棵是我們的朋友\N{\fs13}That one's our friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.61,1:02:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪\N{\fs13}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.27,1:02:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我在這\N{\fs13}I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.05,1:02:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你能讓我媽媽好轉嗎\N{\fs13}Can you do it? Can you make my mum better?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.82,1:02:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你母親能被治愈的話 紫杉樹會那麽做\N{\fs13}If your mother can be healed, the yew tree will do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.82,1:02:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 所以是可以咯? - 你還是不知道你爲什麽召喚我\N{\fs13}- So that's a yes? - You still don't know why you called me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.15,1:02:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有召喚你 就算有也是爲了我媽媽\N{\fs13}I didn't call you. And even if I did, it was obviously for mum.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.90,1:02:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是嗎 - 還能怎麽樣\N{\fs13}- Was it? - What else?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.38,1:02:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那些蠢故事毫無意義\N{\fs13}To listen to idiotic stories that make no sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.89,1:03:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,現在還不是講第三個故事的時候 但快了 在那之後\N{\fs13}It is not yet time for the third tale. But soon. And after that...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.94,1:03:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你要告訴我你的故事 康納·奧馬利\N{\fs13}you will tell me your story, Conor O'Malley.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.74,1:03:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.35,1:03:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是這個 這只是一場噩夢\N{\fs13}No, not this. That's just a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.69,1:03:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣\N{\fs13}No, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.35,1:03:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是真的 那不過是一場噩夢\N{\fs13}That's not my truth. That's just a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.87,1:03:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,然而這會在第三個故事之後發生\N{\fs13}Nevertheless, this will happen after the third tale.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.21,1:03:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道我媽媽會怎麽樣\N{\fs13}I want to know what's going to happen with my mum.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.44,1:03:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,別浪費你被給予的寶貴時間\N{\fs13}Do not waste the precious time that is given you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.36,1:03:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 你要去哪\N{\fs13}Wait. Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.51,1:03:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是治愈之樹 那我需要你去救治\N{\fs13}If you are a tree of healing, then I need you to heal.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.02,1:03:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我會的\N{\fs13}And so I shall.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.37,1:04:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,康納 我會回來的 我保證 你來洛杉磯過聖誕\N{\fs13}Conor, I'll come back. I promise, alright. And you'll come to LA for Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.69,1:04:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想聖誕就留媽媽一個人\N{\fs13}I wont leave mum alone for Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.25,1:04:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 康納你媽媽用的這個藥... - 會讓她好轉\N{\fs13}- Conor this medicine your mum's taking... - Is going to make her well.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.64,1:04:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,康納 很可能不會\N{\fs13}No, Conor, it probably isn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.69,1:04:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 會的 - 這是最後一博了 兒子\N{\fs13}- Yes it is. - No, it's a last stage effort, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.05,1:04:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,會治愈她的 我知道的\N{\fs13}It will heal her. I know it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.50,1:04:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是它來的原因 一定是的\N{\fs13}It is the reason it came. It has to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.75,1:04:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什麽來的原因 - 怪物\N{\fs13}- Reason what came? - The monster.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.50,1:04:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 康納  什麽  - 它總會12點07分出現\N{\fs13}- Conor, what? - It comes to 12h07.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.60,1:04:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,起初我以爲這是一個夢 但它不是\N{\fs13}At first I thought it was a dream, but there is always...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.31,1:04:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,康納 別說了 那是個夢\N{\fs13}Stop. It is a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.04,1:04:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只是個夢 我很抱歉你得面對這件事\N{\fs13}That's all it is. I'm sorry you have to face this...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.41,1:04:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但你得勇敢起來\N{\fs13}but you have to be brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.38,1:04:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,明白嗎\N{\fs13}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.07,1:04:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧\N{\fs13}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.79,1:04:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧\N{\fs13}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.46,1:05:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我會儘快回來\N{\fs13}I'll be back as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.03,1:05:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不够快怎麽辦\N{\fs13}What if it's not fast enough?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.17,1:05:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,康納 聽著\N{\fs13}Conor, listen...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.43,1:05:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 沒事的 - 什麽沒事的\N{\fs13}- It's okay. - What is okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.89,1:05:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,只是...\N{\fs13}Just...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.35,1:05:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用儘快\N{\fs13}You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.65,1:06:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,看到沒\N{\fs13}Look. Do you see it?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.40,1:06:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了嗎 你能揮手嗎\N{\fs13}Do you see it? Can you wave?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.40,1:06:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你能看到他嗎\N{\fs13}Can you see him?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.41,1:06:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,向外婆揮手\N{\fs13}And then we wave to grandma.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.26,1:06:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 外婆\N{\fs13}Hello grandma.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.26,1:06:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,康 向外婆和媽媽打招呼\N{\fs13}Con, you can say hello to grandma and mum?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.68,1:06:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 外婆\N{\fs13}Hello Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.02,1:06:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這就對了\N{\fs13}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.44,1:06:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽已經聽過這個很多次了\N{\fs13}Mum has heard this many times.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.34,1:06:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你準備好了嗎\N{\fs13}Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.34,1:07:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,康 過來\N{\fs13}Con, come sit here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.68,1:07:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,康 看啊\N{\fs13}Con, look.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.52,1:07:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好 外婆  - 媽媽...\N{\fs13}- Hello grandma. - Mama...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.36,1:07:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\fs13}- one... - Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.53,1:07:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs13}There we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.81,1:07:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,外婆 我們在畫畫\N{\fs13}We are doing your picture, grandma.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.62,1:07:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,然後混在一起\N{\fs13}And then mix it together.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.63,1:07:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麽顔色\N{\fs13}What color is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.70,1:07:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,棕色\N{\fs13}Brown.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.64,1:07:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好看又幸運的棕色 - 棕色\N{\fs13}- It is a nice lodgy brown. - Brown.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.64,1:07:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但這裏有棕色了 - 沒錯\N{\fs13}- But we have brown here. - That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.64,1:07:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了嗎\N{\fs13}What can you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.11,1:07:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麽 它們是什麽\N{\fs13}What is that? What are those?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.28,1:07:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得這些是什麽\N{\fs13}What do you... What are these?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.45,1:07:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 眼睛 - 眼睛 沒錯\N{\fs13}- Eyes. - Eyes. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.66,1:07:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,生活永遠都在眼睛之中\N{\fs13}Life is always in the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.77,1:07:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你懂的話\N{\fs13}If you get that...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.34,1:07:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你會是個出色的藝術家\N{\fs13}you will be a proper artist.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.37,1:07:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs13}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.64,1:07:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊\N{\fs13}Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.56,1:07:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這麽畫眼睛\N{\fs13}This is how we draw the eyes in...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.57,1:08:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏是眼睛捕捉映像的地方\N{\fs13}because this is where the eyes catch the reflection.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.70,1:08:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在眼睛裏 我們能看到生活 看見沒\N{\fs13}There we see the life in the eyes. See that?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.70,1:08:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,再來一次 這就是生活\N{\fs13}Do it again. It's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.42,1:08:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,用鉛筆吧\N{\fs13}Maybe if we take a pencil...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.01,1:08:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,然後在那裏畫\N{\fs13}and you can draw on that...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.85,1:08:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,想試試嗎\N{\fs13}Do you want to try it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.27,1:08:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看\N{\fs13}Show me how you do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.76,1:08:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,看 康\N{\fs13}Look, Con.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.51,1:08:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那是他的頭髮 這是他的眉毛\N{\fs13}That's his hair and this is his eyebrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.98,1:08:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊是眼睛\N{\fs13}There's the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.82,1:08:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,看 這是他的嘴\N{\fs13}Oh look, there's his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.74,1:08:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這是他的嘴 他非得憤怒\N{\fs13}There's his mouth. He is very angry.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.58,1:08:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了嗎\N{\fs13}Can you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.92,1:09:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊\N{\fs13}Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.07,1:09:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,然後我們畫張臉\N{\fs13}And then we start to make a face.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.29,1:09:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,然後\N{\fs13}And then...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.51,1:09:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是我們的怪物\N{\fs13}there's our monster.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.93,1:09:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是怪物\N{\fs13}There's the monster.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.69,1:09:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看這怪物\N{\fs13}Look at the monster.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.70,1:09:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,慢點\N{\fs13}Very slowly.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.29,1:09:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣\N{\fs13}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.97,1:10:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 好的\N{\fs13}That's it, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.29,1:10:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,今早是30分鐘的考試\N{\fs13}Okay, so 30 minutes exam this morning...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.91,1:10:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,考的是過去兩周我們都做過的東西\N{\fs13}and this is all the stuff we've been doing for the last two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.92,1:10:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,複習過就不會有意外\N{\fs13}So if you've done your revision, there will be no surprises.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.93,1:10:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你們馬上就得合上書本\N{\fs13}So in a moment I'm going to ask you to turn your pages over.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.20,1:10:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,下面30分鐘都不准說話 要保持完全安靜\N{\fs13}There will be no talking for the next 30 minutes. I want total silence...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.28,1:10:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因爲你們要用的是大腦而不是嘴\N{\fs13}because you are going to use your brains, not your mouths.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.75,1:10:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,30分鐘...\N{\fs13}So 30 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.17,1:10:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,現在開始 祝你們好運\N{\fs13}Starting now. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.58,1:11:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在這麽久之後\N{\fs13}I think I've finally figures you out.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.11,1:11:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我總算搞懂你了\N{\fs13}After all this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.78,1:11:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是想讓人對你印象深刻\N{\fs13}All you're looking for is someone kick your head in.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.37,1:11:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但你知道嗎\N{\fs13}But you know what?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.04,1:11:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不再是那個傢伙了\N{\fs13}I'm not that guy anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.11,1:11:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,再見 奧馬利\N{\fs13}Goodbye, O'Malley.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.26,1:11:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我再也不會看見你\N{\fs13}I no longer see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.18,1:11:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,現在你對我來說是隱形的\N{\fs13}Now you're invisible to me too.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.31,1:11:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你媽媽會好起來\N{\fs13}I hope your mum gets better.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.46,1:12:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麽這麽慢\N{\fs13}What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.49,1:12:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是時候講第三個故事了\N{\fs13}It's time for the third tale.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.61,1:12:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,曾經有個隱形人\N{\fs13}There was once an invisible man...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.94,1:12:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,厭倦了不被人看見\N{\fs13}who was grown tired of being unseen.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.29,1:12:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,實際上 他不是隱形的\N{\fs13}It was not that he was actually invisible.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.88,1:12:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,只是人們習慣于無視他\N{\fs13}It was just the people had become used to not seeing him.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.72,1:12:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天 隱形人再也受不了了\N{\fs13}One day, the invisible man couldn't stand it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.72,1:12:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他好奇如果沒人看見你\N{\fs13}He kept wondering, if no one sees you...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.65,1:12:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那你真的存在嗎\N{\fs13}Are you really there at all?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.32,1:12:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,隱形人做了什麽\N{\fs13}What did the invisible man do?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.68,1:12:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他召喚了怪物\N{\fs13}He called for a monster.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.81,1:13:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道跟你說什麽好 奧馬利\N{\fs13}I don't even know what to say to you, O'Malley.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.19,1:13:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你把他送進了醫院\N{\fs13}You sent him to hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.20,1:13:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他父母威脅要起訴\N{\fs13}His parents are threatening to sue.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.12,1:13:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那不是我 - 什麽\N{\fs13}- It wasn't me. - What was that?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.17,1:13:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是我\N{\fs13}Wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.63,1:13:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是隱形的\N{\fs13}I'm not invisible. I'm not invisible.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.16,1:13:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想被人注意 奧馬利 那可不是最好的辦法\N{\fs13}If you want to be seen, O'Malley, this is not the best way.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.91,1:13:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是隱形的 你聽見了嗎\N{\fs13}I'm not invisible. Did you hear me? I'm not invisible.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.81,1:13:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,根據學校規定 你會被立即開除\N{\fs13}School rules dictate immediately exclusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.07,1:13:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但我是一名教師 我怎麽可能做得到\N{\fs13}But how could I do that and consider myself any kind of a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.91,1:14:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,回去上課吧\N{\fs13}Go back to class.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.63,1:14:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我們改日再談 今天就不談了\N{\fs13}We will talk about this one day, but not today.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.50,1:14:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你不懲罰我?\N{\fs13}You're not punishing me?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.01,1:14:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這有什麽意義\N{\fs13}What could possibly be the point?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.20,1:14:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我來給你們舉個健康情緒的例子\N{\fs13}Well, let me give you an example of emotional wellness.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.95,1:14:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你們知道有時說不是有多困難 對嗎\N{\fs13}You know how difficult it is sometimes to say no. Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.69,1:14:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,而當你們終于有勇氣說出口時 感覺會很棒 這是爲什麽呢\N{\fs13}And how good it feels when you finally find the courage to say it anyway. Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.44,1:14:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你有空嗎\N{\fs13}Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.60,1:14:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麽了\N{\fs13}Hoi, wat is is?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.43,1:14:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我們剛接到醫院電話\N{\fs13}We just got a call from the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.11,1:14:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕康納的母親快不行了 他們想要他過去\N{\fs13}I am afraid that Conor's mother is not going to make it. They want him to come there.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.30,1:15:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你不一起嗎\N{\fs13}Aren't you coming?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.60,1:15:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我就待在這\N{\fs13}I'll be right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.11,1:16:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手怎麽了\N{\fs13}What did you do to your hands?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.72,1:16:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是要談話 對嗎\N{\fs13}It's the talk isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.72,1:16:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,最近每個人都想談話\N{\fs13}Everybody wants to have a talk lately.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.22,1:16:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,康\N{\fs13}Con...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.80,1:16:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,看著我\N{\fs13}Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.47,1:16:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,今早我跟醫生談過話\N{\fs13}I spoke to the doctor this morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.57,1:16:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,新的治療方式沒作用\N{\fs13}The new treatment it's... it's not working.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.76,1:16:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,紫杉樹的那個?\N{\fs13}The one from the yew tree?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.41,1:16:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.93,1:16:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麽會沒作用\N{\fs13}How can it not be working?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.19,1:16:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都發生太快 超出了他們的預想\N{\fs13}Things just happen fast. Faster than they thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.57,1:16:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎麽會沒作用呢 - 不知道\N{\fs13}- How can it not be working? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.99,1:17:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,它必須要有作用\N{\fs13}It has to.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.46,1:17:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那現在怎麽說 下一步怎麽治療\N{\fs13}So what happens now? What's going to be the next treatment?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.39,1:17:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fs13}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.37,1:17:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我一生中從沒這麽抱歉過\N{\fs13}I've never been more sorry about anything in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.01,1:17:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你生氣的話 也沒事 康\N{\fs13}It's okay that you're angry, Con.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.63,1:17:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真的\N{\fs13}It really is.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.89,1:17:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很氣自己告訴你真相\N{\fs13}I'm pretty angry too, to tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.49,1:17:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 康納...\N{\fs13}But Con...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.18,1:17:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,康納 你在聽嗎\N{\fs13}Con, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.87,1:18:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天...\N{\fs13}One day...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.50,1:18:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你回想這件事 爲自己的生氣而感到難過\N{\fs13}if you look back and you feel bad for being so angry...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.71,1:18:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你甚至可以向我傾訴 但你必須清楚 這沒關係\N{\fs13}you couldn't even speak to me, you have to know that was okay...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.98,1:18:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道你會難過\N{\fs13}That I knew.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.27,1:18:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因爲你要對我說的 不用你說出口 我就已經知道了\N{\fs13}Because I know everything you need to tell me without you having to say it out loud.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.00,1:18:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你要摔東西\N{\fs13}And if you need to break things...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.97,1:18:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那就去摔吧\N{\fs13}By God you break them.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.39,1:18:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,使勁摔\N{\fs13}Break them good and hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.38,1:18:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我會伴你左右 康\N{\fs13}And I'll be right there, Con.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.91,1:19:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望我能有100年\N{\fs13}I wish I had a hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.18,1:19:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,能照顧你的100年\N{\fs13}A hundred years I could give to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.09,1:19:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒\N{\fs13}Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.67,1:19:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒\N{\fs13}Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.72,1:19:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒\N{\fs13}Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.19,1:20:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管現在是幾點 你個騙子 醒醒\N{\fs13}I don't care what time it is. You lied. Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.70,1:20:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒\N{\fs13}Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.77,1:20:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我需要你\N{\fs13}I need you now.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.79,1:20:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你再這樣只會讓自己更痛苦 - 沒起作用\N{\fs13}- You are doing yourself more pain. - It did not work.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.73,1:20:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你說紫杉樹會讓她好起來 但幷沒有\N{\fs13}You said the yew tree would make her better, but it did not.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.70,1:20:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,讓她好起來\N{\fs13}Make her better.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.78,1:20:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是你召喚我的 康納·奧馬利\N{\fs13}You're the one who called me, Conor O'Malley.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.58,1:20:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是我召喚你的 那就是爲了救她 爲了治好她\N{\fs13}If I called you, it was to save her. It was to heal her.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.98,1:20:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是來治愈她的 - 你是的\N{\fs13}- I did not come to heal her. - Yes you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.00,1:20:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我是來治愈你的\N{\fs13}I came to heal you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.80,1:20:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我?我不需要治愈\N{\fs13}Me? I'm not the one who needs healing.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.13,1:20:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要我跟你說幾遍啊\N{\fs13}How many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.93,1:20:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我媽媽才是...\N{\fs13}My mum's the one who...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.49,1:21:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,幫幫我\N{\fs13}Help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.84,1:21:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是時候講第四個故事了\N{\fs13}It is time for the fourth tale.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.77,1:21:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 帶我離開這裏\N{\fs13}No, no please. Get me out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.76,1:21:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是時候展現你的噩夢了  - 我必須回到我媽媽身邊\N{\fs13}- It is time for your nightmare. - I need to get back to my mum.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.15,1:21:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,她已經在這裏了\N{\fs13}She is already here.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.90,1:21:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.66,1:21:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽 離開那裏\N{\fs13}Mum, get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.37,1:21:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事\N{\fs13}I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.24,1:21:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的 沒什麽好擔心的\N{\fs13}It is alright. There is nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.27,1:21:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽 快跑 求你了 快跑\N{\fs13}Mum, run. Please, run.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.48,1:21:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\fs13}Mum.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.66,1:21:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\fs13}Mum.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.51,1:21:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,康納\N{\fs13}Conor.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.38,1:22:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\fs13}Mum.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.10,1:22:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.60,1:22:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,康納\N{\fs13}Conor.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.19,1:22:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\fs13}Mum.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.40,1:22:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,康納\N{\fs13}Conor.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.32,1:22:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\fs13}Mum.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.84,1:22:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 別放手 - 不會的\N{\fs13}- Don't let go. - I won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.80,1:22:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 康納  - 媽媽\N{\fs13}- Conor. - Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.68,1:22:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\fs13}Mum.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.11,1:22:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽 不\N{\fs13}Mum, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.82,1:22:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽 不 \N{\fs13}Mum, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.92,1:22:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,康納\N{\fs13}Conor.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.82,1:22:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\fs13}Mum.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.08,1:22:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\fs13}Mum.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.04,1:22:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.00,1:22:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,康納\N{\fs13}Conor.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.22,1:22:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 這是第四個故事  - 快幫忙\N{\fs13}- Here is the fourth tale. - Get help.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.77,1:22:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這是康納·奧馬利的真相\N{\fs13}Here is the truth of Conor O'Malley.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.06,1:22:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 媽媽 - 不\N{\fs13}Mum. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.36,1:22:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 康納 - 這是你的噩夢\N{\fs13}- Mum. - Here is your nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.82,1:22:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 媽媽  - 康納\N{\fs13}- Mum. - Conor.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.92,1:23:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\fs13}Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.38,1:23:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\fs13}Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.21,1:23:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\fs13}Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.09,1:23:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\fs13}Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.71,1:23:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我夢醒的時候\N{\fs13}This is when I wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.43,1:23:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我總是在這時醒來\N{\fs13}This is when I always wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.73,1:23:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,故事還沒講出來\N{\fs13}The tale is not yet told.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.92,1:23:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我離開這裏 我得去見我媽媽\N{\fs13}Get me out of here. I need to see my mum.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.13,1:23:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她再也不在這裏了 康納\N{\fs13}She is no longer here, Conor.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.67,1:24:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,她摔下去了 我沒能拉住她\N{\fs13}She fell. I could not hold onto her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.96,1:24:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,康納\N{\fs13}Conor.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.49,1:24:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 說出真心話  - 不\N{\fs13}- Speak the truth. - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.37,1:24:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你要說出真心話 不然你永遠沒法離開這地方\N{\fs13}You will speak the truth or you will never leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.42,1:24:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什麽真心話 我不知道你什麽意思\N{\fs13}What truth? I do not know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.65,1:24:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我講第四個故事 康納·奧馬利\N{\fs13}You must tell me the fourth tale, Conor O'Malley.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.74,1:24:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你必須跟我講你的噩夢 以免太遲了 - 不行\N{\fs13}- You must tell me your nightmare before it is too late. -No.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.55,1:24:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我 康納 告訴我真心話\N{\fs13}Yes. Tell me, Conor. Tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.70,1:24:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我說的話 它會殺了我 - 你不說 它才會殺了你\N{\fs13}- It will kill me if I do. - It will kill you if you do not.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.53,1:24:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fs13}NO.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.06,1:24:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,說出真心話\N{\fs13}Speak the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.91,1:24:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不行 - 真心話 康納·奧馬利\N{\fs13}- No. - The truth, Conor O'Malley.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.32,1:24:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 告訴我真心話 孩子 - 不行\N{\fs13}- Tell me the truth, boy. - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.34,1:24:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 說出真心話 - 不行\N{\fs13}- Speak the truth. - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.36,1:24:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,說出真心話 孩子\N{\fs13}Speak the truth, boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.56,1:24:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望這一切都結束\N{\fs13}I want it to be over.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.39,1:24:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,知道她快不行了 我承受不住啊\N{\fs13}I can't stand knowing she will go.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.73,1:24:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望這一切都結束​​ 我讓她摔落了\N{\fs13}I want it to be finished. I let her fall.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.07,1:25:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我讓她死了\N{\fs13}I let her die.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.86,1:25:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣很勇敢 康納\N{\fs13}That was brave, Conor.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.69,1:25:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你終于說出來了\N{\fs13}You finally said it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.03,1:25:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,爲什麽它沒殺了我\N{\fs13}Why didn't it kill me?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.03,1:25:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我應該受到懲罰\N{\fs13}I deserve punishment.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.04,1:25:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,受到最重的懲罰\N{\fs13}I deserve the worst.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.88,1:25:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎\N{\fs13}Do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.30,1:25:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都知道她會不行\N{\fs13}I've known forever that she wasn't going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.72,1:25:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,她總跟我說她會好轉\N{\fs13}She keep telling me she was getting better all the time...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.23,1:25:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,因爲那是我想聽的\N{\fs13}because that's what I wanted to hear.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.40,1:26:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信了她\N{\fs13}And I believed her.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.82,1:26:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是不相信\N{\fs13}Except I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.16,1:26:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我開始思考我有多想要這一切都結束\N{\fs13}And I started to think how much I wanted it to be over.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.77,1:26:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒法...\N{\fs13}I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.04,1:26:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒法承受這一切帶給我的孤單\N{\fs13}I couldn't stand how alone that would make me feel.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.26,1:26:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有一部分的你希望這一切都結束 即便這意味著失去她\N{\fs13}Part of you wished it would end even if it meant losing her..
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.13,1:26:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我放手了\N{\fs13}I let her go.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.69,1:26:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我再也撑不住了\N{\fs13}I couldn't hold on for longer...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.03,1:26:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但我總會對她放手\N{\fs13}but I always let her go.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.87,1:26:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是你的真心話 康納·奧馬利\N{\fs13}And that is your truth, Conor O'Malley.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.79,1:26:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我不想這樣\N{\fs13}I don't want it to be though.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.55,1:26:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,現在這一切却成真了\N{\fs13}Now it's for real.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.70,1:26:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,現在她會死 而這是我的錯\N{\fs13}Now she's going to die and it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.51,1:26:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這根本不是全部的真心話\N{\fs13}Now, that is not the truth at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.77,1:26:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是希望結束痛苦 結束你自己的痛苦\N{\fs13}You were merely wishing for an end of pain. Your own pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.81,1:27:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這是人類最原始的心願\N{\fs13}It is the most human wish there is.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.91,1:27:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不是有意如此\N{\fs13}I didn't mean it though.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.32,1:27:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你是的 但也不是\N{\fs13}You did, but you also did not.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.29,1:27:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這兩者怎麽會同時存在\N{\fs13}How can both be true?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.83,1:27:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,王子怎麽會既是殺人犯又受人愛戴呢\N{\fs13}How can a prince be a murderer and beloved by his people?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.80,1:27:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,藥醫師怎麽會既有壞脾氣又有合理的思想呢\N{\fs13}How can an apothecary be evil tempted but right thinking?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.74,1:27:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,隱形人怎麽會讓自己被人看見却愈發孤單\N{\fs13}How can invisible men make themselves lonelier by being seen?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.74,1:27:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 對我來說 你的故事一點都說不通\N{\fs13}I don't know. Your stories never made sense to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.31,1:27:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,因爲人類是複雜的動物\N{\fs13}Because humans are complicated beasts.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.14,1:27:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你清楚知道痛苦真相的同時 却又相信安慰人的謊言\N{\fs13}You believe comforting lies, while knowing full well the painful truth
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.72,1:27:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這讓謊言變得更爲必要了\N{\fs13}that makes those lies necessary.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.10,1:27:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,康納 到頭來 重要的不是你想什麽\N{\fs13}In the end, Conor, it is not important what you think.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.99,1:27:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的僅僅是你做什麽\N{\fs13}It is only important what you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.04,1:27:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那我該做什麽\N{\fs13}So what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.92,1:27:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,做你剛才所做的 你說出了真心話\N{\fs13}What you did just now. You speak the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.26,1:27:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣?\N{\fs13}That's all?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.24,1:27:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得這很容易?\N{\fs13}You think it's easy?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.09,1:27:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你寧願死都不願說\N{\fs13}You were willing to die rather than speak it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.95,1:28:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我好累 這一切讓我好累\N{\fs13}I'm so tired. So tired of all this.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.02,1:28:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,睡吧 還有時間\N{\fs13}Then sleep. There is time.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.87,1:28:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你確定嗎 我得去見我媽媽\N{\fs13}Are you sure? I need to see my mum.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.07,1:28:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 今晚我們都會見到她 - 你也會在嗎\N{\fs13}- We will both see her tonight. - Will you be there?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.91,1:28:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\fs13}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.99,1:28:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那將是我的最終之行\N{\fs13}It will be the final steps of my walking.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.33,1:28:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,第四個故事會怎麽結束\N{\fs13}How does the fourth story end?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.67,1:28:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,睡吧\N{\fs13}Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.51,1:28:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,睡吧\N{\fs13}Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.35,1:28:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,睡吧\N{\fs13}Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.52,1:29:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,謝天謝地 康納 康納\N{\fs13}Thank God. Conor! Conor!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.52,1:29:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我找你快找瘋了\N{\fs13}I've been out of my mind trying to find you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.41,1:29:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我還有些事得做 - 沒時間了 現在必須走了\N{\fs13}- There was something I had to do. - No time. We have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.89,1:29:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,該死\N{\fs13}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.73,1:29:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,外婆\N{\fs13}Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.78,1:29:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs13}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.45,1:29:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,客廳和所有的事 我都很抱歉\N{\fs13}About the living room and the everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.85,1:29:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係\N{\fs13}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.85,1:30:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係\N{\fs13}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.02,1:30:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,康納 你和我...\N{\fs13}You know, Conor. You and me...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.07,1:30:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我們很難相處 對嗎\N{\fs13}we're not the most natural fit, are we?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.85,1:30:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.17,1:30:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得是很難\N{\fs13}I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.59,1:30:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我也這麽覺得\N{\fs13}I guess not either.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.35,1:30:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但我們必須學會相處\N{\fs13}But we're going to have to learn.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.11,1:30:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我知道 - 你真的知道 對嗎\N{\fs13}- I know. - You do know, don't you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.37,1:30:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,當然了\N{\fs13}Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.38,1:30:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我們有一個交集\N{\fs13}But there is one thing we have in common.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.96,1:30:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你的媽媽\N{\fs13}Your mum.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.75,1:31:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她就是我們的交集\N{\fs13}That's what we have in common.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.02,1:32:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事\N{\fs13}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.73,1:32:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,看來你找到他了\N{\fs13}I see you found him.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.74,1:32:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fs13}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.14,1:32:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 親愛的\N{\fs13}Hello my darling.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.90,1:32:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 媽媽? - 是的 我在\N{\fs13}- Mum? - Yes, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.65,1:32:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我在了 能感覺到我的手嗎\N{\fs13}I'm here. Can you feel my hand?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.08,1:32:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,康納也在\N{\fs13}Conor's here too.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.67,1:32:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是嗎 - 沒錯\N{\fs13}- Is he? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.27,1:32:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,康納\N{\fs13}Conor.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.65,1:33:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏就是故事的結局\N{\fs13}Here is the end of the tale.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.58,1:33:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我好怕\N{\fs13}I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.59,1:33:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你當然會怕\N{\fs13}Of course you're afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.89,1:33:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這很不容易 遠遠沒那麽容易\N{\fs13}It will be hard. It will be more than hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.87,1:33:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但你會挺過去 康納·奧馬利\N{\fs13}But you will make it through, Conor O'Malley.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.08,1:33:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你會待著嗎\N{\fs13}You'll stay?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.88,1:33:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在這裏\N{\fs13}I will be right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.57,1:34:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我該做什麽\N{\fs13}What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.13,1:34:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,現在剩下的就是說出最簡單的真心話\N{\fs13}Now all that is left is for you to speak the simplest truth of all.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.17,1:34:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望你離開\N{\fs13}I don't want you to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.27,1:34:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 親愛的\N{\fs13}I know, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.14,1:34:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望你離開\N{\fs13}I don't want you to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.45,1:35:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,第四個故事怎麽結尾的\N{\fs13}How does the fourth story end?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.56,1:35:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,男孩緊緊地抱著他的母親\N{\fs13}It ends with a boy holding on tight to his mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.77,1:35:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子...\N{\fs13}And by doing so...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.87,1:36:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他就終于能放手了\N{\fs13}he can finally let her go.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.05,1:36:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,康納\N{\fs13}Conor.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.09,1:36:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這是你的房間了\N{\fs13}This is your room now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.58,1:36:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在爲你準備\N{\fs13}I've been making it ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.48,1:37:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fs13}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.99,1:38:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,麗茲·克萊頓
